('IT005','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/l/a/lasra_sofa_1s.jpg','                                     LASRA SOFA 1S                                ','IDR 8,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 8.000.000 - Standard Fabric OP05 THANOS C/L9</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 8.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 9.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 9.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric S: Rp 11.500.00</li>  </ul>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team  </p>  <p>The name of LASRA is taken from Arabic which means a good kinship. The modular system of this L shape sofa allows you to configure and suit the space. You can change the leg rest ottoman from left to right or center, you can also use this to give more seating space when gathering with more people. We use soft density for our sofa cushioned and low side armrest to give you more leisure and comfortable experience.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (770 (W) x 825 (D) x 740 (H)) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Shell Finish Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Thanos C/L9 (Fabric A)  <p><em>* Fabric option are available </em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane dark brown color open pore (OP05) with glides  <p><em>* Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
('IT006','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/l/alara_sofa_1s_-_thanos_c_e4_1_1__2.jpeg','                                     ALARA SOFA 1S                                ','IDR 8,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 8.000.000 - Standard Fabric OP05 THANOS C</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 8.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 9.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 9.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric S: Rp 11.500.00</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team <br />The name of ALARA is taken from Arabic which means rest. The modular system of this L shape sofa allows you to configure and suit the space. You can change the leg rest ottoman from left to right or center, you can also use this to give more seating space when gathering with more people. We use soft density for our sofa cushioned and low side armrest to give you more leisure and comfortable experience.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (825 (W) x 810 (D) x 735 (H) ) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Shell Finish: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Thanos C/E4 (Fabric A)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available </em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg: Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane dark brown color open pore (OP05) with glides  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  </ul>  <ul>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
