('IT009','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/c/u/cubo_sofa_1s-1.jpg','                                     CUBO SOFA 1S                                ','IDR 8,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>INTRODUCING, L SERIES!</p>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team</p>  <p>Cubo comes fromt the English word \"Cube\" which refer to the overall form of the sofa. Cubo is made out of wood panels layered with mindi veneer with white wash finish. This simple but cute sofa is great addition to your living space.</p>  <p>L Series comes with living, and bedroom collection. You also can change the fabric upholstery to make this furniture very personal with your style and concept.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm) : 750 (W) x 700 (D) x 700 (H) Seat Height 410</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Shell Frame and Structure : Plywood - MDF panel base</li>  <li>Shell Cover : Exposed panel by covered by mindi veneer in polyurethane white wash color (VOP-MIWW)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat Cushion : Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Velma Grey (Fabric A)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Back Cushion : Full dacron with removeable upholstery in fabric Velma Grey (Fabric A)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg : Steel square tube in black color (ME-B) with glides.   <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
