('IT013','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/c/h/charlotte_sofa_1seater_1.jpg','                                     CHARLOTTE SOFA 1S                                ','IDR 9,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 9.000.000 - Standard Fabric Devano Gray</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 10.000.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 11.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 12.000.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 14.500.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 24.500.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Rest &amp; Relax at Home with Charlotte Sofa</p>  <p>Inspired by one of modern city in US, Charlotte own modern minimalism design and feels homey. Accommodate your simplicity and space saving living style, this sofa can transform to be a sofa bed, perfect for gathering with friends and family also quick nap or long sleep. Charlotte Sofa is available in 3 size and multifunction ottoman for leg rest or coffee table.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (1050 (W)  x 850 (D) x 750 (H)) </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood panel base.</li>  <li>Base, Back Cushion, and Armrest Cover: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery.</li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Back Cushion: Full dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Base leg: Plywood base glider in black finish.</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p></div> ','CA001'),
('IT014','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/r/arma_sofa_1s_1.jpeg','                                     ARMA SOFA 1S                                ','IDR 9,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>ARMA collection comes in with a modern but simple and functional design to help users embrace humility. In this age where the pace of life move quickly, peacefulness and quiteness are often underappreciated.</p>  <p>Aram (calm) is a name derived from the Persian word the ARMA.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension : 750 (W) x 815 (D) x 750 (H) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 9.000.000 - Standart Fabric Elijah 201</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 9.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 10.000.000 </li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 10.500.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 12.000.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification :</p>  <ul>  <li>Wood Frame: Solid Mahogany Wood - Finishing Walnut Red.</li>  <li>Armrest Pad: Laminated Rattan - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Backrest Frame: Laminated Rattan - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Backrest Cover: Skin Off Rattan Frame &amp; Fitrit Closed Weaving - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Seatrest: Removeable Cushion, Webbing Base - Fabric Elijah 201.</li>  <li>Backrest: Removeable Cushion, Full Dacron - Fabric Elijah 201.</li>  <li>Note : Small pillow is not included.</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
('IT015','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/c/e/cesto_sofa_1s_terracre_2.jpg','                                     CESTO SOFA 1S - TERRACOTA CREAM                                ','IDR 9,400,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p>Made using hi-quality outdoor materials such as ropes and metals. Our braided &amp; twisted ropes are made using polypropylene materials, which recyclable and nature friendly. Our outdoor furniture series are able to provide aesthetically pleasing and best furniture solution for both indoor and outdoor space.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 750 (W) x 770 (D) x 770 (H) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <style type=\"text/css\"><!--  p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #454545} li.li1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #454545} ul.ul1 {list-style-type: disc}  --></style>  <p>Materials :</p>  <ul>  <li>Backrest Frame : Aluminum round tube</li>  <li>Backrest Cover : Flat rope weaving in terracota cream color.</li>  <li>Cushion : Webing strap base and normal foam combination with removable upholstery in outdoor fabric Cartenza148</li>  <li>Pillow : Full dacron with removable upholstery in outdoor fabric Cartenza148</li>  <li>Base Leg - Aluminum round tube</li>  <li>3 small pillows included</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
