('IT017','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/1/2/12_3_.jpg','                                     CHESTER SOFA 1S                                ','IDR 10,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 10.500.000 - Standard Fabric Vegan Leather Bostonia Dark Brown</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 11.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 12.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 13.500.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 16.000.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 25.500.000</li>  </ul>  <p>Mid Century Modernism through Chester Sofa</p>  <p>Chester was known as historical city in England for its beauty of mid century building. Transformed the mid century modernism, Chester sofa beautifully captured elegant &amp; modernity through the entire room. Made by vegan leather standard upholstery and classic timeless design, Chester Sofa is a perfect sofa to beautify your living room. This sofa has a wide arm design, comfortable for headrest, and is available in 3 sizes + multifunction ottoman.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (1050 (W)  x 850 (D) x 750 (H)) </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood panel base.</li>  <li>Base, Back Cushion, and Armrest Cover: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery.</li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Back Cushion: Full dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Base leg: Steel rectangular pipe and steel plate in black mate powder coating</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p></div> ','CA001'),
('IT018','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/k/a/kasha_sofa_2s_wo_arm_1_.jpg','                                     KASHA SOFA 2S WITHOUT ARM                                ','IDR 11,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 10.000.000  </li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 11.000.000 - Standard Fabric Elena Almond</li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 12.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 13.000.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 16.700.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 26.500.000</li>  </ul>  <p>AKARA Series</p>  <p>AKARA Series was designed by VIVERE Design Team. The name, AKARA was taken from Sanskrit which means “come back home”. We believe that people always miss the home comfort. Bringing comfortability inside your house, we are adding the feature and homey characteristic to each design.  Simple yet contemporary, it is also represents unique detail to accentuate elegant touch. All design is very suitable for space saving home in urban &amp; modern environment.  These series comes in modular design to fits perfectly to your available space.</p>  <p>KASHA Sofa is a modular sofa. You can combine sofa modules to fit in your living space such as:<br />- L Shape<br />- U Shape<br />- C Shape<br />- U Shape with Daybed<br />- L Shape with Daybed<br />- Long Sofa<br />- Corner Sofa<br />- 1S Lounge Sofa<br />- And many more!</p>  <p>Mix and match every modules of KASHA Sofa and make your own modular sofa style! Show your creation, show your creativity, and enjoy the living experience!</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): ( 1300 (W)  x 780 (D) x 750 (H) ) - Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg: Solid Sungkai, finishing Akara Dark Brown OP (glossiness 5%), PU Coating</li>  <li>Cushion: Laminated Foam, Fabric Upholstery (Elena Almond — B)</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
