('IT024','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/c/h/charlotte_sofa_2_seater_2.jpg','                                     CHARLOTTE SOFA 2S                                ','IDR 14,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 14.000.000 - Standard Fabric Devano Gray</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 15.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 17.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 18.500.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 23.000.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 39.000.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Rest &amp; Relax at Home with Charlotte Sofa</p>  <p>Inspired by one of modern city in US, Charlotte own modern minimalism design and feels homey. Accommodate your simplicity and space saving living style, this sofa can transform to be a sofa bed, perfect for gathering with friends and family also quick nap or long sleep. Charlotte Sofa is available in 3 size and multifunction ottoman for leg rest or coffee table.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (1700 (W)  x 850 (D) x 750 (H)) </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood panel base.</li>  <li>Base, Back Cushion, and Armrest Cover: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery.</li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Back Cushion: Full dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Base leg: Plywood base glider in black finish.</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p></div> ','CA001'),
