('IT027','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/k/a/kasha_sofa_2s_1_.jpg','                                     KASHA SOFA 2S                                ','IDR 14,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 12.500.000  </li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 14.000.000 - Standard Fabric Elena Almond</li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 15.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 17.000.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 19.600.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 30.800.000</li>  </ul>  <p>AKARA Series</p>  <p>AKARA Series was designed by VIVERE Design Team. The name, AKARA was taken from Sanskrit which means “come back home”. We believe that people always miss the home comfort. Bringing comfortability inside your house, we are adding the feature and homey characteristic to each design.  Simple yet contemporary, it is also represents unique detail to accentuate elegant touch. All design is very suitable for space saving home in urban &amp; modern environment.  These series comes in modular design to fits perfectly to your available space.</p>  <p>KASHA Sofa is a modular sofa. You can combine sofa modules to fit in your living space such as:<br />- L Shape<br />- U Shape<br />- C Shape<br />- U Shape with Daybed<br />- L Shape with Daybed<br />- Long Sofa<br />- Corner Sofa<br />- 1S Lounge Sofa<br />- And many more!</p>  <p>Mix and match every modules of KASHA Sofa and make your own modular sofa style! Show your creation, show your creativity, and enjoy the living experience!</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): ( 1520 (W)  x 780 (D) x 750 (H) ) - Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg: Solid Sungkai, finishing Akara Dark Brown OP (glossiness 5%), PU Coating</li>  <li>Cushion: Laminated Foam, Fabric Upholstery (Elena Almond — B)</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
('IT028','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/l/i/livia_2s__l_series_1.jpg','                                     LIVIA SOFA 2S                                ','IDR 14,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>INTRODUCING, L SERIES!</p>  <p>New line of compact living furniture series To accommodate compact living era, which smaller and space saving furniture are the most wanted items for millennial, L Series are the products that fits you the most! With lighter looks furniture, simple and minimalist design, but still comfortable and fully usage are the soul of L Series.</p>  <p>Our RnD team do an end to end research to build this furniture, VIVERE long lasting quality with affordable price.</p>  <p>L Series comes with living, and bedroom collection.</p>  <p>You also can change the fabric upholstery to make this furniture very personal with your style and concept</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 12.000.000 </li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 14.000.000 - Standard Fabric Sanny 180/Viena Custard</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 16.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 18.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric Special : IDR 22.000.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 38.000.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm) : 1490 (W) x 770 (D) x 770 (H) – Seat Height 410</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Shell Frame and Structure : Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Shell Cover Normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Sanny 180.   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat Cushion : Multidensity normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Sanny 180.   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Back Cushion : Full dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Viena Custard.   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg : Natural Mindi in polyurethane color.   <p><em>*Wood a