('IT029','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/m/a/maha_accent_chair_wlnt_fabric_2_9.jpg','                                     MAHA ACCENT CHAIR                                ','IDR 14,300,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 13.200.000</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 13.800.000</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 14.300.000 - Standard fabric as on photo</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 14.900.000</li>  <li>Fabric Special: IDR 16.000.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 25.900.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Designed by Yuni Jie, a comfortable sofa, with \"Bold\" and elegant design. Good for your Living Room, timeless design. With its rich texture, MAHA living collection brings warm, calm, and inviting feel to space. The overall collection is as a fresh approach for urban contemporary design. The look is very much international without forgetting organic design linen adapted from local culture.</p>  <p><br />Dimension (mm): 835 (W) x 830 (D) x 795 (H) - Seat Height 410 </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Wood Base Leg, Armrest, and Backrest Frame: Solid wood frame</li>  <li>Frames Finish: Exposed panel covered by walnut veneer in polyurethane gold walnut color (VOP-WG)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Multi-density normal foam, dacron, and plywood base with fixed upholstery in fabric Pure Velvet023 (Fabric C)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Back Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Pure Velvet023 (Fabric C)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
