('IT031','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/l/a/lasra_sofa_3s.jpg','                                     LASRA SOFA 3S                                ','IDR 15,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 15.000.000 - Standard Fabric OP05 THANOS C/L9</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 16.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 17.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 18.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric S: Rp 21.500.00</li>  </ul>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team  </p>  <p>The name of LASRA is taken from Arabic which means a good kinship. The modular system of this L shape sofa allows you to configure and suit the space. You can change the leg rest ottoman from left to right or center, you can also use this to give more seating space when gathering with more people. We use soft density for our sofa cushioned and low side armrest to give you more leisure and comfortable experience.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (1800 (W) x 825 (D) x 740 (H)) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Shell Finish Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Thanos C/L9 (Fabric A)  <p><em>* Fabric option are available </em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane dark brown color open pore (OP05) with glides  <p><em>* Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
('IT032','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/l/alara_sofa_3s_-_thanos_c_e4_1_1_.jpeg','                                     ALARA SOFA 3S                                ','IDR 15,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 15.000.000 - Standard Fabric OP05 THANOS C</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 16.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 17.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 18.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric S: Rp 21.500.00</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team <br />The name of ALARA is taken from Arabic which means rest. The modular system of this L shape sofa allows you to configure and suit the space. You can change the leg rest ottoman from left to right or center, you can also use this to give more seating space when gathering with more people. We use soft density for our sofa cushioned and low side armrest to give you more leisure and comfortable experience.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (1855 (W) x 810 (D) x 735 (H))– Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Shell Finish: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Thanos C/E4 (Fabric A)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available </em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg: Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane dark brown color open pore (OP05) with glides  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  </ul>  <ul>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA001'),
('IT033','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/r/arma_sofa_2s_-_a.jpeg','                                     ARMA SOFA 2S                                ','IDR 15,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>In this age where the pace of life move quickly, peacefulness and quiteness are often underappreciated.</p>  <p>ARMA collection comes in with a modern but simple and functional design to help users embrace humility.</p>  <p>Aram (calm) is a name derived from the Persian word the ARMA.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension : 1380 (W) x 815 (D) x 750 (H) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 15.000.000 - Standart Fabric Elijah 201</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 15.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 16.000.000 </li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 16.500.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 18.000.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification :</p>  <ul>  <li>Wood Frame: Solid Mahogany Wood - Finishing Walnut Red.</li>  <li>Armrest Pad: Laminated Rattan - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Backrest Frame: Laminated Rattan - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Backrest Cover: Skin Off Rattan Frame &amp; Fitrit Closed Weaving - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Seatrest: Removeable Cushion, Webbing Base - Fabric Elijah 201.</li>  <li>Backrest: Removeable Cushion, Full Dacron - Fabric Elijah 201.</li>  </ul>  <p>Note : Small pillow is not included.</p></div> ','CA001'),
