('IT035','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/1/_/1_6__1.jpg','                                     CHESTER SOFA 2S                                ','IDR 16,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 16.000.000 - Standard Fabric Vegan Leather Bostonia Dark Brown</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 17.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 19.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 20.500.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 24.500.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 39.000.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Chester was known as historical city in England for its beauty of mid century building. Transformed the mid century modernism, Chester sofa beautifully captured elegant &amp; modernity through the entire room. Made by vegan leather standard upholstery and classic timeless design, Chester Sofa is a perfect sofa to beautify your living room. This sofa has a wide arm design, comfortable for headrest, and is available in 3 sizes + multifunction ottoman.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (1700 (W)  x 850 (D) x 750 (H)) </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Frame and Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood panel base.</li>  <li>Base, Back Cushion, and Armrest Cover: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery.</li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Back Cushion: Full dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Base leg: Steel rectangular pipe and steel plate in black mate powder coating</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p></div> ','CA001'),
