('IT091','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/s/e/seville_side_table_b.jpg','                                     SEVILLE SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 3,400,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Elegant Shape of Seville Side &amp; Coffee Table</p>  <p>Presenting Plaza de Espana, also known as Spain Square, a well-known monument in Seville, Spain. The Plaza de Espanas main feature were massive, towering columns, which resembled the shape of Sevilles coffee and side tables. Touched by a solid mahogany wood black finish combined with Quadra Carlo Moreno Polish as the top to create an elegant design.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 400 (W) x 400 (D) x 600 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg: Solid mahogany wood as body in black mate open pore texture PU finishing, glossiness 15%</li>  <li>Top Table: 9mm Sintered Stone - Carlo Moreno* by Quadra. Finishing shiny polished, creating a mirror-like shine that is identical or smoother than naturally polished rock.</li>  <li>Grain will be provided randomly</li>  <li>Adjustable black plastic glides</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p></div> ','CA002'),
('IT092','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/4/_/4_5__2.jpg','                                     LUCCA SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 3,700,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Stay Classy with Lucca Coffee &amp; Side Table</p>  <p>As historical city in coastal Central Italy, Lucca is best known as mid century wall which build around the city. The walls were surrounded the old town, as the city expanded and modernized until today. Adopting the spirit of this city, Lucca Coffee &amp; Side Table maintained it well by giving classic yet elegant touch into its design by using steel pipe leg and dual layer shelving. There is also extra storage space with lower shelving to manage your belongings. Certainly, Lucca can create new atmosphere into your existing space.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm) : Dia. 350 x 550 (H) </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Top Table &amp; Shelf Structure: Plywood and MDF panel base</li>  <li>Top Table &amp; Shelf Finish: Exposed panel covered by white ash veneer in polyurethane gold brown color.</li>  <li>Base Leg: Steel round pipe and steel plate in black matte powder coating.</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA002'),
('IT093','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/r/a/raska_side_table_2_.jpg','                                     RASKA SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 4,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>AKARA Series</p>  <p>AKARA Series was designed by VIVERE Design Team. The name, AKARA was taken from Sanskrit which means “come back home”. We believe that people always miss the home comfort. Bringing comfortability inside your house, we are adding the feature and homey characteristic to each design.  Simple yet contemporary, it is also represents unique detail to accentuate elegant touch. All design is very suitable for space saving home in urban &amp; modern environment.  These series comes in modular design to fits perfectly to your available space.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): ( 410 (W) x 410 (D) x 500 (H) )</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg: Solid Sungkai, finishing Akara Dark Brown OP (glossines 5%), PU Coating</li>  <li>Top Table : Solid Surface Top, Tulip Design</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA002'),
