('IT099','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/r/o/roosa_side_table_1.jpg','                                     ROOSA SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 5,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this dining table.</p>  <p>And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes our HiCraft Rattan collection suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p><em>*For project only, MOQ term and condition apply</em></p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 600 (W) x 600 (D) x 400 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Top Table Frame : Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane black color open pore. </p>  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Top Table : 8mm clear tempered glass.</p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Bottom Shelf : Solid mahogany wood frame and mdf with mahogany veneer laminate in black color open pore. </p>  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available (must be same with top table frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane black color open pore with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available (only applied on frame with same color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA002'),
