('IT113','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/s/o/sola_coffee_table_1_1.jpg','                                     SOLA COFFEE TABLE                                ','IDR 8,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>The name SOLA means sun in English and in Bahasa means Matahari. The key features in this product are its weaving pattern, which made from several materials and gives a special effect.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 1300 (W) x 800 (D) x 360 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Top Table Structure : MDF base with mahogany wood edging and  mahogany veneer laminate.</p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Top Table Finish : Exposed panel covered by mahogany veneer in polyurethane grey color open pore. </p>  <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane grey color open pore with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available (must be same with top table color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA002'),
