('IT115','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/r/a/raska_coffee_table_1_.jpg','                                     RASKA COFFEE TABLE                                ','IDR 9,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>AKARA Series</p>  <p>AKARA Series was designed by VIVERE Design Team. The name, AKARA was taken from Sanskrit which means “come back home”. We believe that people always miss the home comfort. Bringing comfortability inside your house, we are adding the feature and homey characteristic to each design.  Simple yet contemporary, it is also represents unique detail to accentuate elegant touch. All design is very suitable for space saving home in urban &amp; modern environment.  These series comes in modular design to fits perfectly to your available space.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): ( 1200 (W) x 600 (D) x 400 (H) )</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg: Solid Sungkai, finishing Akara Dark Brown OP (glossines 5%), PU Coating</li>  <li>Top Table : Solid Surface Top, Tulip Design</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA002'),
