('IT119','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_mekar_coffee_table_2.jpg','                                     MEKAR COFFEE TABLE                                ','IDR 10,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Mekar coffee table calls for attention. Mekar is a statement piece constructed from 2 cm diameter rattan stems, lined and bent gracefully to resemble a blooming flower.</p>  <p>Welcoming anyone who comes into the room where these tables stand. Mekar - which means “blooms” in the Indonesian language - comes in two sizes.</p>  <p>Design by Alvin T.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension : 745 (Dia.) x 385 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials :</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner Structure: Plywood frame.</li>  <li>Backrest: Skin On Open Weaving Kembang Tanjung - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Top Table: Plywood - MDF covered by walnut veneer recon laminate - finishing walnut gold.</li>  <li>Shell Decoration: Skin off rattan pole - finishing natural to light brown.</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p><br /><br /><br /></p></div> ','CA002'),
