('IT157','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/w/h/whatsapp_image_2020-10-15_at_14.27.48_27.jpeg','                                     NAGATA ROCKING CHAIR                                ','IDR 6,100,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>The name NAGATA is taken from Sanskrit words mean look forward to the future. The most interesting features are the modern contemporary chic design and the side swivel ornaments.</p>  <p>Design by Rina Renville (Anja Studio).</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 580 (W) x 780 (D) x 800 (H) – Seat Height 450</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in light grey color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Decoration : Skin off (polished) rattan core with leather binding in light grey color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available (must be same with shell frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Cushion : Normal foam with removable upholstery in fabric Kolon104 Cream. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Skin off (polished) rattan pole with leather binding in dark brown color with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available (must be same with shell frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Sled : Mahogany wood in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available (must be similiar with shell frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p> </p></div> ','CA004'),
('IT158','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/h/o/holly_arm_chair_2_1.jpg','                                     HOLLY ARMCHAIR                                ','IDR 6,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><style type=\"text/css\"><!--  p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Arial; color: #424242} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Arial; color: #424242; min-height: 14.0px}  --></style>  <p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 5.700.000</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 6.100.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 6.500.000 - Standard Fabric Pazzion</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 6.900.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 8.100.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 11.700.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>S Series 2 Collection</p>  <p>Enriched the S Series Collection</p>  <p>With brand new items that have just been launched in mid-2017, S Series line will accentuate your living sanctuary to look modern and contemporary drastically. </p>  <p>This addition to existing line is also aimed to give warmth and freshness in your rooms. Playful &amp; colorful life, unique pattern &amp; color for your home which gives fun and cheerful ambiance into your rooms. Last but not least you still can mix and match the products with many styles of your home. </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm):  555 (W) x 560 (D) x 770 (H) – Seat Height 450</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Shell Frame and Structure : Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>  <p>Shell Cover : Multidensity normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Pazzion01A. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Seat Cushion : Multidensity normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Pazzion01A.</p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Wood Base Leg : Solid wood frame in dark grey color. </p>  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT159','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_mizu_lounge_chair_2.jpg','                                     MIZU LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 6,800,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes our HiCraft Rattan collection suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension : 630 (W) x 750 (D) x 800 (H) – Seat Height 420mm</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Frame: Skin Off Rattan - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Backrest: Skin On Open Weaving Kembang Tanjung - Finishing Natural.</li>  <li>Seatrest: Fixed Cushion - Fabric Elijah C181</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p><br /><br /><br /></p></div> ','CA004'),
('IT160','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/e/l/elwood_lounge_chair_1.jpg','                                     ELWOOD LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 7,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>ELWOOD  is inspired by a little suburb in Melbourne, Australia.</p>  <p>Just like the characteristics of the suburb, ELWOOD is a lounge chair that is quaint but playful at the same time. Its design features include a bulbous frame, kembang tanjung rattan weaving, and a chunky cushion, which allows the chair to be delightful to sit on.</p>  <p>ELWOOD lounge chair is a terrific addition to create a bright and cheerful space.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 800 (W) x 695 (D) x 780 (H) - Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials :</p>  <ul>  <li>Top Frame: Skin off (polished) rattan pole in grey wash color   <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  <p><em>*Also available in full skin on version</em></p>  </li>  <li>Shell Cover: Skin on rattan peel open weaving in natural color   <p><em>*Rattan weaving color option are available (only applied on frame with same color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Normal foam and dacron with removeable upholstery in fabric Viena Custard   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Pillow: Full dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Viena Custard   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg: Mahogany wood in grey wash color with glides   <p><em>*Solid wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p><br /><br /><br /></p></div> ','CA004'),
('IT161','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/l/altona_lounge_chair_1.jpg','                                     ALTONA LOUNGE CHAIR WITH METAL LEG                                ','IDR 7,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>ALTONA is a lounge chair inspired by the seaside industrial suburbs in Australia.</p>  <p>Just like the suburbs, ALTONA lounge chair is robust with its sturdy construction and elegance with its curvaceous body.</p>  <p>The kembang tanjung rattan weaving pattern on the backrest add more character in this piece to a wonderful addition any family space</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 790 (W) x 815 (D)  x 780 (H) - Seat Height 420</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Top Frame and Decoration: Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  <p><em>*Also available in full skin on version</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Back Cover: Skin on rattan peel open weaving in natural color </p>  <p><em>*Weaving color option are available (only applied on frame with same color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Seat Cushion: Normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Hazael163</p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Pillow: Full dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Hazael163 </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg: Steel round tube in black U (dark grey) color with glides </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT162','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/i/m/img_2207_24.jpg','                                     ELI ARM CHAIR                                ','IDR 7,100,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 6.900.000</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 7.100.000 - Standard Fabric Rich Mermaid</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 7.300.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 7.500.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 12.400.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 11.000.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">S Series Collection<br />Introducing the new furniture collection from VIVERE<br />Embellished with a strong line and designed with modern and elegant taste, S Series will fit seamlessly in your home.<br />Craftily designed by our designer, this collection will bring fresh look to your space</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Dimension (mm): 690 (W) x 630 (D) x 760 (H) – Seat Height 420</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Frame: Solid sungkai wood frame</li>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Finish: Natural sungkai in polyurethane color (SW-SN) Wood and finishing option are available   <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat and Back Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Rich Mermaid (Fabric B)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT163','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/s/asiento_lounge_chair_-_b.jpg','                                     ASIENTO LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 7,300,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes our HiCraft Rattan collection suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by Wolf Doser.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 795 (W) x 800 (D) x 800 (H) – Seat Height 420</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Shell and Armrest Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in havana brown color.   <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Shell Decoration : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in havana brown color.   <p><em>*Rattan weaving color option are available (only applied on frame with same color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>Cushion : Normal foam and dacron with fixed removable upholstery in fabric Porfido085.   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg : Steel round tube in black color with glides.   <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT164','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/l/i/lisbon_lounge_chair.jpg','                                     LISBON LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 8,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 8.000.000 - Standard Fabric Hillary Quary</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 8.500.000 </li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 9.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 9.500.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 11.000.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 16.500.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Modern Tranquility with Lisbon Lounge Chair</p>  <p>Lisbon was known as capital city of Portugal, a harbor city in Southern Europe. Relaxing, retro and modern are the major key point of Portugal captured well on our Lisbon Lounge Chair. Adding up adjustable headrest cushion feature to maximize its comfort, bring more uniqueness into this chair. Supported by high back rest design for more comfort seating and also - Seamless strap with magnetic hold for adjustable head cushion, mainly becomes important note to address the comfort of this product. It is also suitable to be mix and match with Charlotte sofas as living room set.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): (690 (W)  x 890 (D) x 1050 (H)) </p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Shell Frame and Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Shell Cover: Normal foam with fixed upholstery</li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery</li>  <li>Throw Pillow &amp; Head Pad: Full dacron with removable upholstery.</li>  <li>Wood Base Leg: Solid mahogany wood frame in polyurethane dark black color</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p></div> ','CA004'),
('IT165','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/c/a/calantha_lounge_chair_2.png','                                     CALANTHA LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 8,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The term CALANTHA comes from the Greek language which means blossom. CALANTHA has a distinct elegance due to its collar - like backrest and its nude rattan finishing. Its collar is inspired by blooming flower petals. Its beautiful shape, combined with steel frames and manau rattan, gives a fashionable attitude to any room.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 800 (W) x 700 (D) x 850 (H) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Backrest Frame Skin off (polished) rattan pole frame in natural color</li>  <li>Seat Cushion Plywood base, normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Rich Pearl (fabric B)</li>  <li>Back Cushion Normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in same fabric</li>  <li>Leg Frame Steel round tube in dark grey (Black U) color with glides</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT166','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_tortue1_1.jpg','                                     TORTUE LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 8,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>The grid silhouette of TORTUE Lounge Chair was inspired from the shell of a Tortoise, or Tortue in French word.</p>  <p>TORYUE Lounge Chair consist of one frame module act as both seat and backrest, the curvy shape gives a comfortable and safe feeling as is being hugged, similar to the function of a tortoise shell.</p>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm) : 840 (W) x 800 (D) x 850 (H) – Seat Height 410</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material:</p>  <div>  <ul>  <li>Seatrest and Backrest Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole frame in natural color.</li>  <li>Seat and Back Cushion : Normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Abihud (Fabric A).</li>  <li>Pillow : Full dacron with removable upholstery in same fabric.</li>  <li>Leg Frame : Steel round tube in dark grey (Black U) color with glides.</li>  </ul>  </div></div> ','CA004'),
('IT167','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_portabella_loung_chair_-_b.jpg','                                     PORTABELLA LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 8,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>The name PORTABELLA is taken from a type of mushroom species, portabello mushroom.</p>  <p>The most interesting features in this product are the exposed rattan frame which inspired by the mushrooms grill and its finely made cushion shapes as it is blooming.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 830 (W) x 830 (D) x 780 (H) – Seat Height 420</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell and Armrest Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in grey wash color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Cover : Normal foam with fixed upholstery in fabric Hansel Neptune. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Seat Cushion : Normal foam with removable upholstery in fabric Hansel Neptune. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Steel round tube in black U (dark grey) color with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT168','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_leyye_lounge_chair.jpg','                                     LEYYE LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 8,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>The name LEYYE is inspired by the way people in relaxing way or in Bahasa called leyeh-leyeh.</p>  <p>The most interest features in this product are the unusual shape but really comfortable to sit in several seating positions and the fitrit weaving on the whole chair.</p>  <p>Design by Rina Renville (Anja Studio)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 1000 (W) x 750 (D) x 820(H) – Seat Height 410</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in combination color (orange and light grey). </p>  <p><em>*Combination color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Cover : Skin on rattan fitrit weaving in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Cushion : Normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Elijah140.</p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Steel round tube in grey color with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT169','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/k/a/kayra_lounge_chair.jpg','                                     CASAKA - KAYRA LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 6,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>CASAKA is an Indonesian woodcraft furniture brand established in 2013 which focused on natural and solid wood furniture. CASAKA believes in the synergy of quality and aesthetics that every furniture is an artwork that should serve both functions, not only impressive but also long-lasting and sustainable.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Every piece tells a story.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Solid wood is a genuinely natural product and each area demonstrates a unique structure and color dominated by the location of the tree as well as weather and ground conditions. The delicate branches, cracks, intergrown areas and overlaps demonstrate the material’s authenticity, that’s why every piece of wood is unique and has their own personality and the different story one from another.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">And we proudly announce that since 2019 CASAKA is a part of VIVERE Group. Find out CASAKA Collection on the nearest VIVERE Showroom.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">------</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Dimension: 660 x 575 x 690mm</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Teak wood</li>  <li>Natural color</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT170','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_volare_chair_2.jpg','                                     VOLARE LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 9,400,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>VOLARE taken from Italian words which means \"To Fly\". A beautiful and elegant wing chair concept with natural materials.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 830 (W) x 800 (D) x 1100 (H) – Seat Height 400</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Cover : Skin on rattan peel open weaving in natural color.</p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Cushion : Plywood base and normal foam with fixed upholstery in fabric Elijah140 - Fabric Type A. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Steel plate in white color with glides with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT171','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/c/o/cofano_1_seat_1_1_.jpg','                                     COFANO SOFA 1S - TERRACOTA CREAM                                ','IDR 9,700,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>COFANO, in italian means “hood” the name and design was inspired by a traditional Indonesia’s food cover called “tudung saji”.</p>  <p>Tudung saji is widely use by Indonesian to protect food from fly or insects. Influence with the tudung character, Cofano sofa was designed to make everyone who sit feels comfortable and safe.</p>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 895 (W) x 790 (D) x 815 (H) Seat Height 400mm</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material:</p>  <ul>  <li>Aluminium frame. Seat cushion in outdoor fabric. Ropes binding backrest in white cream color</li>  <li>Standard Fabric: Cartenza143</li>  <li>Standard Ropes: Terracota Cream</li>  <li>1 pillow included</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT172','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/w/i/wing_chair_2_9.jpg','                                     WING CHAIR                                ','IDR 11,600,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 4 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 10.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 11.600.000 - Standard Fabric as on photo</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 12.700.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 13.800.000</li>  <li>Fabric Special : IDR 20.400.000</li>  <li>Leather : IDR 40.200.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Single chair for your living room or study room accent. Adapted from Classic Wing Chair, but we modified it with little touch and care to be modern than before. An Elegant look will fulfill your room</p>  <p> <br />Dimension (mm): 710 (W) x 870 (D) x 1200 (H) – Seat Height 430</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification</p>  <ul>  <li>Solid nyatoh wood and plywood for the frame</li>  <li>Webbing suspension and medium density foam for cushioning, wrapped with dacron, finished with selected fabric </li>  <li>Solid legs, close pore surfaces finished using PU material, salak brown color</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
('IT173','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_mika_lounge_chair_-_b.jpg','                                     MIKA LOUNGE CHAIR                                ','IDR 13,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 13.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 13.500.000 - Standard Fabric Rich Othello</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 14.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 15.000.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 18.000.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 22.500.000</li>  </ul>  <p>  </p>  <p class=\"p1\">S Series Collection<br />Introducing the new furniture collection from VIVERE<br />Embellished with a strong line and designed with modern and elegant taste, S Series will fit seamlessly in your home.<br />Craftily designed by our designer, this collection will bring fresh look to your space</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Dimension (mm): 750 (W) x 815 (D) x 760 (H) – Seat Height 380</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Frame: Solid sungkai wood frame</li>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Finish: Natural sungkai in polyurethane color (SW-SN)   <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat and Back Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Rich Othello (Fabric B)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA004'),
