('IT175','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/i/m/img_2215_9.jpg','                                     RAYA ARM CHAIR                                ','IDR 18,200,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Special: IDR 18.200.000 - Standard Fabric - Fabric BEIGE070 (Standard)</li>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 15.400.000</li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 16.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 16.500.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 17.100.000</li>  <li>Fabric SPECIAL (S) : Rp 17.100.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 24.200.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Designed by Yuni Jie. Inspired by the beauty and richness of Indonesian culture, the RAYA collection embraces both function and aesthetic, transforming living essentials into elegant masterpieces. Intertwined between the traditional and the modern, RAYA is a celebration of style and luxury.</p>  <p><br />Dimension (mm): 720 (W) x 800 (D) x 1030 (H) - Seat Height 450</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Frame: Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base</li>  <li>Frame Finish: Exposed panel finished in polyurethane dark brown color (VOP-S)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Shell Cover: Synthetic rattan peel open weaving in dark brown color</li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Multi-density normal foam and dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Beige070 (Fabric Special)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Pillow: Full dacron with removable upholstery in fabric Beige070 (Fabric Special)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 33px; top: 264px;\"> </div></div> ','CA004'),
('IT176','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/c/i/cielo_dining_table_4s.jpg','                                     CIELO DINING TABLE 4S                                ','IDR 6,100,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this dining table. And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes our HiCraft Rattan collection suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 1000 (W) x 1000 (D) x 750 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Top Table Structure : Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane black color open pore. </p>  <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Solid mahogany wood in polyurethane black color open pore with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Wood color and finishing option are available (must be same with top table color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p> </p></div> ','CA005'),
