('IT227','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/e/gesture_1.jpg','                                     STEELCASE - WK GESTURE CHAIR                                 ','IDR 26,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Adaptive yet dynamic to conquer the working environment these days, Steelcase Gesture Chair is the first office chair designed to support a greater range of postures and user sizes. Within a better understand on human posture and inspired by human body, this chair is fully supported healthy movement by its 3D liveback system and availability of 360 degree armrest motion. It also can reflect a well qualified chair to achieve long time goals to its users.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimensions (mm): (568.3 (W) x 533.4 (D) x 997 - 1123.5 (H) )<br /><br />Seat Height ( Lowest to Highest): (407 - 5334 mm (H) )<br /><br /></p>  <p>Gesture Chair Feature &amp; Benefit :</p>  <ul>  <li>Supporting Heathy Movement</li>  <li>3D Liveback System</li>  <li>Greater Range of User Sizes</li>  <li>360°degree armrest motion<br /><br /></li>  </ul>  <p>Gesture Chair Material Description :</p>  <ul>  <li>Frame Finish : Black Plastic</li>  <li>Seat Finish : Upholstery Ebony Omni R</li>  <li>Back Finish : Ebony Omni R</li>  <li>Base Type : Black Plastic</li>  <li>Shell Finish : Black</li>  <li>Arm Type : 360 Arm</li>  <li>Castor : Hard Castors</li>  </ul></div> ','CA006'),
('IT228','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/1/4/145.jpg','                                     VIVERE x SEVEN SAGES - SOAP INSECTICIDAL SOAP FOR PLANTS SETOF3 BLACK                                ','IDR 68,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Transform Your Mood &amp; Productivity with Seven Sages</p>  <p>Concerning on our wellbeing and health, Seven Sages has fully aware the need of proper skincare and understanding on the products that applied to our skin. They produce natural soap pack which relaxing and soothing to calm your day. Various soap choices, from rose geranium, bergamout, insecticidal, memphis and lavandula will be a perfect remedy to reduce stress of busy day. Most importantly, all of the products are chemical free, natural humectants, hot process, using essentials oils, squeaky clean and zero plastic.</p>  <p><br /><br />Used for:</p>  <ul>  <li>Pest infested plants</li>  <li>Quarantine of new plants</li>  <li>Very dirty leaves</li>  <li>3 Insecticidal bar Soap @25g each.</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Warning:</p>  <ul>  <li>Use only in evenings as soap contains photosensitive Neem oil</li>  <li>Do not use on sensitive leaves such as some fragile begonias, thin-leafed calatheas, P.Verrucosum etc...</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Ingredients and Benefits:</p>  <ul>  <li>Saponified coconut oil - Cleans leaves with natural anti-fungal and anti-bacterial properties. No oily residue is left behind after rinse.</li>  <li>Neem oil - Eliminates all pests and mild anti-fungal properties.</li>  <li>Peppermint - Pests hate the smell of peppermint and will be unlikely to return.</li>  <li>Activated charcoal - Anti-fungal and anti-bacterial<br /><br /></li>  </ul>  <p>How to Use:</p>  <ul>  <li>Wet leaves and wet the soap bar</li>  <li>Take 2-3 seconds to lather up soab bar in your hands, you should get a lot of foam</li>  <li>Soap up the leaves with your hands gently but thoroughly, be sure to get the underside of leaves too.</li>  <li>Rinse off thoroughly</li>  <li>Wipe gently until it is dry.<br />(If you soap up too many plants in one go, your fingers might get pruny (wrinkled), this is normal and we encourage you to soap up plants in small numbers with rest in between.)</li>  </ul></div> ','CA007'),
