('IT384','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/b/a/bambino_barstool_1.jpg','                                     BAMBINO BARSTOOL                                ','IDR 3,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes our HiCraft Rattan collection suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension : 500 (W) x 500 (D) x 910 (H) – Seat Height 795</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials :</p>  <ul>  <li>Frame: Skin off rattan - finishing havana brown.</li>  <li>Seatrest &amp; Back cover: Skin on open weaving kembang tanjung - finishing natural.</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT385','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/k/a/kallista_side_chair_1.jpg','                                     KALLISTA SIDE CHAIR                                ','IDR 3,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The name Kallista derives from the ancient Greek word \"Kalliste\" which means \"most beautiful\".</p>  <p>As its names suggest, Kallista is a beautiful side chair to be included in any dining room. Although the design is simple, its curvaceous frame adorns with kembang tanjung rattan weaving makes the design versatile and adaptable.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 595 (W) x 620 (D) x 820 (H) - Seat Height 470</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials :</p>  <ul>  <li>Leg and Frame: Skin off (polished) rattan pole in black color   <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  <p><em>*Also available in full skin on version</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat and Back Cover: Skin on rattan peel open weaving in natural color   <p><em>*Rattan weaving color option are available (only applied on frame with same color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT386','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/e/s/esca_side_chair_-_2_1_.jpg','                                     ESCA ARMCHAIR                                ','IDR 3,800,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>INTRODUCING, L SERIES!</p>  <p>Design by VIVERE Design Team</p>  <p>Esca derives from an Irish Gaelic word “Easca” which means easy. Just like its meaning, Esca Dining Chair was designed with simple look in mind. This simplicity in its aesthetic enables the chair to be combined with various types of dining table.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 550 (W) x 540 (D) x 805 (H) – Seat Height 445</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Leg and Frame: Steel round tube dark grey/black u color (ME-BU) with glides   <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seatrest and Backrest Base: 1 piece bent plywood with exposed sungkai veneer in polyurethane medium brown color (BP-SMB)   <p><em>*Bent plywood color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seatrest and Backrest Cushion: Normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Daphnie Onyx (Fabric A)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT387','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/v/a/vassa_side_chair_2_9.jpg','                                     VASSA SIDE CHAIR                                ','IDR 3,900,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 3.900.000 - Standard Fabric Rover 130</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 4.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 4.200.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 4.300.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 6.900.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 5.300.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Designed by Irvan Noeman. Contemporary look with natural style furniture, Good for your modern dining room or office chair.</p>  <p> <br />Dimension (mm): 510 (W) x 515 (D) x 865 (H) - Seat Height 440</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Frame: Solid wood frame</li>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Finish: Exposed panel covered by walnut veneer in water-based red walnut color (VOP-WR)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Plywood base, normal foam, and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Rover130 (Fabric A)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT388','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/v/i/vinta_side_chair_2_.jpg','                                     VINTA DINING CHAIR                                ','IDR 4,300,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 6 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: Rp 4.000.000  </li>  <li>Fabric B: Rp 4.300.000 - Standard Fabric Elena Mid Gray</li>  <li>Fabric C: Rp 4.600.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: Rp 4.900.000</li>  <li>Special: Rp 5.800.000</li>  <li>Leather: Rp 8.200.000</li>  </ul>  <p>AKARA Series</p>  <p>AKARA Series was designed by VIVERE Design Team. The name, AKARA was taken from Sanskrit which means “come back home”. We believe that people always miss the home comfort. Bringing comfortability inside your house, we are adding the feature and homey characteristic to each design.  Simple yet contemporary, it is also represents unique detail to accentuate elegant touch. All design is very suitable for space saving home in urban &amp; modern environment.  These series comes in modular design to fits perfectly to your available space.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): ( 500 (W)  x 585 (D)  x 880 (H) ) -  Seat Height 460</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material &amp; Finishing :</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg: Solid Sungkai, finishing Akara Dark Brown OP (glossiness 5%), PU Coating</li>  <li>Cushion: Laminated Foam, Fabric Upholstery (Elena Mid Grey — B)</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT389','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/n/a/naru_side_chair_-_b_31.jpg','                                     NARU SIDECHAIR                                ','IDR 4,300,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>The name Naru is inspired from guitar strings, which apply to the seat frame with small rattan core. The most interesting feature are the rattan repetitive U Shape and its modern contemporary design.</p>  <p>Design by Abie Abdillah.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 580 (W) x 585 (D) x 955 (H) – Seat Height 450</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell and Armrest Frame: Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Decoration: Skin off (polished) rattan core in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available (must be same with shell frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Cushion: Normal foam with removable upholstery in fabric Ace11 Mineral. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg: Steel round tube in white color with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT390','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/m/a/matala_counterstool_-_b_16.jpg','                                     MATALA COUNTERSTOOL                                ','IDR 4,300,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Matala is truly inspired by the concept of a smart living and office, creating balance and promoting harmony.</p>  <p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair.</p>  <p>And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes Matala suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by (Late) Irvan Noeman.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 520 (W) x 530 (D) x 880 (H) – Seat Height 660</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Decoration : Skin off (polished) rattan core in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available (must be same with shell frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Cushion : Normal foam with removable upholstery in fabric Pattaya Dark Grey/Ash. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Steel round tube in grey color with glides </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT391','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/m/a/matala-barstool_16.jpg','                                     MATALA BARSTOOL                                ','IDR 4,400,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Matala is truly inspired by the concept of a smart living and office, creating balance and promoting harmony.</p>  <p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair. And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes Matala suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by (Late ) Irvan Noeman.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 520 (W) x 530 (D) x 980 (H) – Seat Height 760</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell Frame : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Decoration : Skin off (polished) rattan core in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available (must be same with shell frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Cushion : Normal foam with removable upholstery in fabric Pattaya Bright Olive. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg : Steel round tube in bright green color with glides. </p>  <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT392','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/m/a/matala-side-chair_16.jpg','                                     MATALA SIDE CHAIR                                ','IDR 4,400,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Matala is truly inspired by the concept of a smart living and office, creating balance and promoting harmony.</p>  <p>The transformation of Indonesian tradition into a product with contemporary design spirit, by fusing the high manufacturing process and the high craftsmanship of the locals, as well as the detail of Indonesian rattan, has brought the real beauty and comfort to this chair. And yet, its attention to the detail of human factors makes Matala suitable for supporting your productive days at the office or your lazy weekends at home.</p>  <p>Design by (Late) Irvan Noeman.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 510 (W) x 625 (D) x 830 (H) – Seat Height 480</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell Frame: Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Decoration: Skin off (polished) rattan core in natural color. </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available (must be same with shell frame color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Cushion: Normal foam with removable upholstery in fabric Pattaya Chilli Red. </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg: Steel round tube in red chilli color with glides.</p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT393','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/t/attwood_side_chair_1.jpg','                                     ATTWOOD SIDE CHAIR                                ','IDR 4,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>ATTWOOD name is derived from a Melbourne suburb, just like its sister Elwood lounge chair.</p>  <p>In comparison to its sibling, ATTWOOD is more mature and elegant. Its design features include sturdy wooden legs as the foundation and a rattan structured backrest that envelops the seating.</p>  <p>The addition of rattan fitrit weaving allows the chair to have warm attributes to it.</p>  <p>These features create a robust but serene piece of dining chair that could add elegance to dining experience.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 565 (W) x 560 (D) x 765 (H) - Seat Height 450</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Top Frame and Decoration: Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color </p>  <p><em>*Rattan color option are available</em></p>  <p><em>*Also available in full skin on version</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Cover: Skin off (polished) rattan fitrit weaving in natural color</p>  <p><em>*Rattan weaving color option are available (only applied on frame with same color)</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Back Cushion: Normal foam and dacron with removeable upholstery in fabric Yoel163 </p>  <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Base Leg: Mahogany wood in black color with glides </p>  <p><em>*Solid wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p><br /><br /></p></div> ','CA011'),
('IT394','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/j/u/julia_side_chair_2_27.jpg','                                     JULIA SIDE CHAIR                                ','IDR 4,800,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 4.400.000</li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 4.800.000 - Standard Fabric Rich Mermaid</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 5.200.000</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 5.600.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 8.800.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 6.600.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">S Series Collection<br />Introducing the new furniture collection from VIVERE<br />Embellished with a strong line and designed with modern and elegant taste, S Series will fit seamlessly in your home.<br />Craftily designed by our designer, this collection will bring fresh look to your space</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Dimension (mm): 480 (W) x 575 (D) x 880 (H) – Seat Height 480</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Frame: Solid sungkai wood frame</li>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Finish: Natural sungkai in polyurethane color (SW-SN)   <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat and Back Cushion: Normal foam and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Rich Mermaid (Fabric B)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT395','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/n/e/new_project_45__1.jpg','                                     SADHA SIDE CHAIR                                ','IDR 5,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>As the name suggests, Sadha comes from Sanskrit word means bound together. The idea is to combine more than one materials with one intention, which is to create a diversity in material selection to create an elegant yet subtle furniture.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Product Dimension (mm) : 640 (W) x 640 (D) x 840 (H) – Seat Height 470</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Backrest Frame: Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color (RC-N)</li>  <li>Backrest Cover: Skin off (polished) rattan fitrit weaving in natural color</li>  <li>Armrest Pad: Solid teak wood in brown jati color (SW-TN)   <p><em>*Wood and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Cushion: Plywood base and normal foam with fixed upholstery in fabric Twice Lime (Fabric B)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg: Steel round tube in black color (ME-B) with glides   <p><em>*Metal color option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT396','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/p/i/pigura_dining_chair_1.jpg','                                     CASAKA - PIGURA SIDE CHAIR                                ','IDR 4,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Pigura means frame or the artwork(picture) itself. The concept of this solid wood chair is see-through and light, simple yet elegant. We hope it will complete your home, just like PIGURA.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">CASAKA is an Indonesian woodcraft furniture brand established in 2013 which focused on natural and solid wood furniture. CASAKA believes in the synergy of quality and aesthetics that every furniture is an artwork that should serve both functions, not only impressive but also long-lasting and sustainable.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></p>  <p class=\"p1\">Every piece tells a story.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Solid wood is a genuinely natural product and each area demonstrates a unique structure and color dominated by the location of the tree as well as weather and ground conditions. The delicate branches, cracks, intergrown areas and overlaps demonstrate the material’s authenticity, that’s why every piece of wood is unique and has their own personality and the different story one from another.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></p>  <p class=\"p1\">And we proudly announce that since 2019 CASAKA is a part of VIVERE Group. Find out CASAKA Collection on the nearest VIVERE Showroom.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">------</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Dimension: 450 x 550 x 955 mm</p>  <p class=\"p1\"> </p>  <p class=\"p1\">Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Jati or teak wood first class</li>  <li>Natural - polyurethane finishing</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
('IT397','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/v/a/vassa_side_chair_2_9_2.jpg','                                     VASSA SIDE CHAIR -  WLNT KOLON104                                ','IDR 4,200,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Available in 5 Fabrics option:</p>  <ul>  <li>Fabric A: IDR 3.900.000 </li>  <li>Fabric B: IDR 4.000.000</li>  <li>Fabric C: IDR 4.200.000 - Standard Fabric WLNT KOLON104</li>  <li>Fabric D: IDR 4.300.000</li>  <li>Leather: IDR 6.900.000</li>  <li>Special: IDR 5.300.000</li>  </ul>  <p> </p>  <p>Designed by Irvan Noeman. Contemporary look with natural style furniture, Good for your modern dining room or office chair.</p>  <p> <br />Dimension (mm): 510 (W) x 515 (D) x 865 (H) - Seat Height 440</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Frame: Solid wood frame</li>  <li>Base Leg and Backrest Finish: Exposed panel covered by walnut veneer in water-based red walnut color (VOP-WR)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Seat Cushion: Plywood base, normal foam, and dacron with fixed upholstery in fabric Rover130 (Fabric A)   <p><em>*Fabric option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA011'),
