('IT497','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/a/r/arus_side_table_2_.jpg','                                     CASAKA - ARUS SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 3,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Arus means “flow” in Bahasa, it is shown with the flowing grain of the wood. The flow grain elevate the smooth and elegant feel of the table.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">CASAKA is an Indonesian woodcraft furniture brand established in 2013 which focused on natural and solid wood furniture. CASAKA believes in the synergy of quality and aesthetics that every furniture is an artwork that should serve both functions, not only impressive but also long-lasting and sustainable.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Every piece tells a story.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Solid wood is a genuinely natural product and each area demonstrates a unique structure and color dominated by the location of the tree as well as weather and ground conditions. The delicate branches, cracks, intergrown areas and overlaps demonstrate the material’s authenticity, that’s why every piece of wood is unique and has their own personality and the different story one from another.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">And we proudly announce that since 2019 CASAKA is a part of VIVERE Group. Find out CASAKA Collection on the nearest VIVERE Showroom.</p>  <p class=\"p1\">------</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Dimension: 390 x 390 x 440 mm</p>  <p class=\"p1\">Materials:</p>  <ul>  <li>Jati or teak wood</li>  <li>Natural - polyurethane finishing</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA013'),
('IT498','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/v/a/vassa_side_table_wlnt_1_9.jpg','                                     VASSA SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 5,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Inspired by the nation artistic character that commonly practices carving or crafting,<br />the main character of Vassa lays in its intricate slices or bevel detail.</p>  <p><br />Dimension (mm): 600 (W) x 600 (D) x 350 (H)<br /> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Top Table Structure: MDF panel base</li>  <li>Top Table Finish: Exposed panel covered by walnut veneer in water-based red walnut color (VOP-WR)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Base Leg Structure: Solid wood frame with glides</li>  <li>Base Leg Finish: Frame covered by walnut veneer in water-based red walnut color (VOP-WR)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA013'),
('IT499','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/n/i/nitara_side_table_1.jpg','                                     NITARA SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 6,000,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>NITARA is a name derived from a Kannada - India word niratara, which means continuous.</p>  <p>The name refers to a design feature of the collection: a continuous shape in NITARA coffee and side table. It is shown through the cylinder base, which is made of simple veneer laminating, further emphasizing continuity.</p>  <p>Design by Alvin T.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 450 (W) x 450 (D) x 520 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials :</p>  <ul>  <li>Inner structure: Plywood frame.</li>  <li>Body cover: White ash veneer recon laminate - finishing dark grey.</li>  <li>Top Table: Solid Surface.</li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA013'),
('IT500','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/m/a/maha_side_table_1_9.jpg','                                     MAHA SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 7,200,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Designed by Yuni Jie. Timeless design furniture collection with its rich texture. <br />MAHA living collection brings warm, calm, inviting feel to space. An overall collection is a fresh approach to urban contemporary design.<br />International look product without forgetting organic design linen adapted from local culture.<br /><br /></p>  <p>Dimension (mm): 440 (W) x 440 (D) x 600 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Material Specification:</p>  <ul>  <li>Case Structure: Solid wood frame and plywood - MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Side Decoration Cover: MDF panel base.</li>  <li>Case and Side Cover Finish: Exposed panel covered by walnut veneer in polyurethane gold walnut color (VOP-WG)   <p><em>*Veneer and finishing option are available</em></p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul></div> ','CA013'),
('IT501','https://dsfun9g7xo5tj.cloudfront.net/media/catalog/product/cache/36dac68969ef38d465ffe279f20fd09b/g/d/gdi_mekar_side_table_1.jpg','                                     MEKAR SIDE TABLE                                ','IDR 7,500,000','         <h4>Product Description</h4>     <div class=\"value\" ><p>Good Design Indonesia (GDI) is a national scale awarding event that given to the best design works in Indonesia. This program organized by the Directorate General of National Export Development (DJPEN), the Ministry of Trade of Republic of Indonesia, since 2017.<br />The GDI winners are divided into three categories: GDI of the Year, GDI Best and GDI.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>MEKAR side table calls for attention. Mekar is a statement piece constructed from 2 cm diameter rattan pole, lined and bent gracefully to resemble a blooming flower.</p>  <p>Welcoming anyone who comes into the room where these tables stand. MEKAR - which means “blooms” in the Indonesian language - comes in two sizes.</p>  <p>Design by Alvin T.</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Dimension : 495 (Dia.) x 545 (H)</p>  <p> </p>  <p>Materials :</p>  <ul>  <li>  <p>Shell Frame : Plywood shell and frame.</p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Shell Cover and Top Table : Walnut veneer in polyurethane brown color.</p>  </li>  <li>  <p>Decorative Shell : Skin off (polished) rattan pole in natural color.</p>  </li>  <li>Made in Indonesia</li>  </ul>  <p><br /><br /><br /></p></div> ','CA013');
